## PROJECT COST SUMMARY (from image reference)
  Domain               : ₹1,900
  Backend development  : ₹5,000
  Frontend development : ₹4,000
  Third-party APIs     : ₹3,500 (OpenAI, S3, Resend)
  Documentation:
    - API Integration  : Included in dev cost
    - Project Book     : ₹500-1,000 (printing/binding)
    - PPT Presentation : ₹0 (Canva free)
  ─────────────────────────────
  TOTAL                : ~₹15,400

## KEY FEATURES IMPLEMENTED ACROSS MVPs
  ✓ AI Resume Parsing (GPT-4o-mini extracts skills, experience, education)
  ✓ AI Job Matching (0-100% match score per candidate per job)
  ✓ Candidate Ranking (auto-rank applicants by AI score)
  ✓ Role-Based Auth (JWT, Job Seeker vs Recruiter)
  ✓ Resume Upload (PDF/DOCX, max 5MB, cloud storage)
  ✓ Job Post Management (multi-step form, draft/publish)
  ✓ Applicant Pipeline (filter by status, score, bulk actions)
  ✓ Email Notifications (signup, application, status changes)
  ✓ Responsive Design (mobile + tablet + desktop)
  ✓ Swagger API Docs + Postman Collection

## IMPORTANT NOTES
  - "Apply" button on the landing page requires login/signup (from image)
  - Limited job listings shown publicly on landing page (teaser)
  - Full job access requires account
  - AI costs capped at ₹2,500/month with fallback to keyword matching
  - All file uploads stored on AWS S3 with signed URLs for private access

## HOW TO START
  1. Read MVP1-foundation-landing-page.todo → Set up project structure
  2. Complete each MVP in order (1 → 7)
  3. Mark tasks [ ] → [x] as you finish them
  4. Each MVP builds on the previous — don't skip!
